      | Tomas has been involved with INEX for quite a few years now (almost too long to recall). He's been a part of the team that prepares the future workcamp leaders for their roles since 2006 and he's lead four volunteer projects in the Czech Republic so far. He's a Computer Sciences graduate from the Charles University of Prague and he enjoys good food, travelling, badminton and (of course) giraffes.

